    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, presenting as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, showroom-quality shine, and the interior is pristine, showing absolutely no signs of wear. Every component, from the engine to the electronics, functions perfectly, offering the experience of a brand-new car for its next owner.",
