    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for those needing a functional daily driver. The exterior shows its age with some clear coat peeling on the roof and a few minor dents along the passenger side. Inside, the upholstery has some noticeable staining and a small tear on the driver's seat. Mechanically, it runs well, though it will likely need a suspension refresh and new tires in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets the job done without any frills.",
      "price": 21000.0,
