    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all hobbyists and restoration fans! This vehicle is the perfect project for anyone looking to roll up their sleeves and bring a classic back to its former glory. While it's currently in poor condition and needs significant work, it offers a fantastic foundation for a complete rebuild or a valuable source for authentic parts. Grab this opportunity to create something truly unique at a great price!",
